\f0\b\fs44 \cf2 \cb1 1. Executive Summary\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs32 \cf2 The Backlog Orchestrator is an AI-powered offshore inspection management system built with CrewAI. This project proposes integrating the Agent2Agent (A2A) protocol to transform the monolithic CrewAI system into a distributed, interoperable multi-agent architecture. Each discipline-specific agent (Topsides, FUIMS, PSV, Subsea, Pipeline, Corrosion, Methods) will be wrapped as an independent A2A server, enabling cross-framework communication, dynamic orchestration, and future-proof scalability.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 Key Business Value:
\f2\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Interoperability:
\f2\b0 \'a0Agents can communicate with any A2A-compliant system (Google ADK, Microsoft Agent Framework, BeeAI)\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Scalability:
\f2\b0 \'a0Individual agents can be updated, scaled, or replaced independently\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Discoverability:
\f2\b0 \'a0Each agent exposes capabilities via standard AgentCards\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Future-Proofing:
\f2\b0 \'a0Ready for ecosystem integration without vendor lock-in\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
